Reuters reports that the online meeting led by the United States restricted synthetic drug flow was held on Friday (July 7), and at least 84 countries will participate. Toddrobinson, assistant Secretary of State of the United States State Department, said that China said on the eve of the meeting that China needs to do more to cut off the supply chain of illegal synthetic drugs.

