#### Why do you want to provide such weapons now?

For more than a year, the United States has used its traditional 155mm grenade guns and ammunition inventory, and has transported more than 2 million ammunition to Ukraine. Allies around the world also provide additional ammunition.

The 155mm ammunition can combat the target of 24-32 kilometers, so that it is the preferred ammunition for the Ukrainian ground forces trying to combat enemy targets from a long distance. The Ukrainian army consumed thousands of bullets in the battle with the Russians every day.

