After this analysis, it is enough to prove that although Yi Gang and Li Xiaopeng were arranged to be re -positioned in March this year, the Xi Jinping authorities obviously considered that both of them would not be in office and insisted on finishing the next five years. On the premise, Li Xiaopeng's term will be longer than Yi Gang. After all, Li Xiaopeng will be only 65 years old next year.On July 5, 2023, Pan Gongsheng, Secretary of the Party Committee of the People's Bank of China and director of the State Foreign Exchange Bureau, met with the visited President of the Austrian Central Bank Holzman. The two sides exchanged opinions on the economic and financial issues that were concerned about.

